Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: Image4Layer
Version: 0.43.4
Summary: It is implemented by 'pillow' in blend mode of CSS3. And more...
Home-page: https://github.com/pashango2/Image4Layer
Author: Toshiyuki Ishii
Author-email: pashango2@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: Image4Layer
        ===========
        
        It is implemented by 'pillow' in blend mode of CSS3. And more...
        
        Install
        =======
        
        ::
        
            pip install image4layer
        
        Usage
        =====
        
        .. code:: python
        
            from PIL import Image
            from image4layer import Image4Layer
        
            source = Image.open("tests/ducky.png")
            backdrop = Image.open("tests/backdrop.png")
        
        .. code:: python
        
            Image4Layer.__version__
        
        ::
        
            '0.43'
        
        Separable blend modes
        =====================
        
        normal
        ~~~~~~
        
        .. code:: python
        
            Image4Layer.normal(backdrop, source)
        
